msgid ""
"Whether to assume the system clock is unsynced. This applies to the "
"ratelimit handling code. If this is set to ``True``, the default, then the "
"library uses the time to reset a rate limit bucket given by Discord. If this "
"is ``False`` then your system clock is used to calculate how long to sleep "
"for. If this is set to ``False`` it is recommended to sync your system clock "
"to Google's NTP server."
msgstr ""

